                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-209-off1105 t18170416-209-crimeloc1107"></join>. On the 17th of April, about five o'clock, the prisoner came into my house and had some beer; he paid for it, and went to the back-door, as I thought, to go out. In about two or three minutes, I saw him come up the kitchen stairs and go out. I followed him, and took the coat and tin case from him. They were my <rs id="t18170416-209-viclabel1108" type="occupation">servant</rs>
